123
00:06:19,379 --> 00:06:20,580
Did you forget?

124
00:06:20,580 --> 00:06:22,215
Tomahawk steak...

125
00:06:22,215 --> 00:06:23,850
This isn't a dream.

126
00:06:23,850 --> 00:06:26,653
I have no idea what you're talking about.

127
00:06:26,653 --> 00:06:29,355
