129
00:06:33,626 --> 00:06:35,528
Hama-chan!

130
00:06:38,231 --> 00:06:40,667
Hama-chan!

131
00:06:40,667 --> 00:06:42,035
- Hama-chan!
- What?

132
00:06:42,035 --> 00:06:44,637
