133
00:06:44,637 --> 00:06:45,872
Where's your injury?

134
00:06:45,872 --> 00:06:48,174
What injury?

135
00:06:48,174 --> 00:06:49,542
Weren't we on the main island yesterday?

136
00:06:49,542 --> 00:06:51,711
And then I went to the police station...

137
00:06:51,711 --> 00:06:53,446
- You seemed to have gotten into a fight.
- I'm very busy today.

138
00:06:53,446 --> 00:06:56,382
If you need something, tell me when I'm back.

139
00:06:57,751 --> 00:06:59,219
Just let me talk for a second.

140
00:06:59,219 --> 00:07:01,020
Hama-chan!

141
00:07:11,631 --> 00:07:14,466
