142
00:07:15,435 --> 00:07:16,503
Where are you going?

143
00:07:16,503 --> 00:07:17,871
I've been looking for you for so long.

144
00:07:17,871 --> 00:07:19,539
- What do you want?
- Something's gone wrong!

145
00:07:19,539 --> 00:07:20,607
