146
00:07:20,607 --> 00:07:22,275
I was clearly on the main island last night.

147
00:07:22,275 --> 00:07:24,411
But I woke up today back on Starry Islet!

148
00:07:24,411 --> 00:07:25,512
Me, too.

149
00:07:25,512 --> 00:07:27,113
