back to Starry Islet.

150
00:07:27,113 --> 00:07:29,583
You too?

151
00:07:29,583 --> 00:07:30,583
What should we do?

152
00:07:30,583 --> 00:07:32,452
Does this have to do with
wishing on a shooting star?

153
00:07:32,452 --> 00:07:34,621
Wishing upon a shooting star?

154
00:07:34,621 --> 00:07:36,089
How did you know I made a wish?

155
00:07:36,089 --> 00:07:37,089
Are you an idiot?

156
00:07:37,089 --> 00:07:38,324
We made it together.

157
00:07:38,324 --> 00:07:40,593
I never made a wish with you.

158
00:07:40,593 --> 00:07:42,829
Remember that night
we had the roadside banquet?

159
00:07:42,829 --> 00:07:44,130
Your mom shoved a microphone at us,

160
00:07:44,130 --> 00:07:45,365
